ivardefs.name: comment
ivardefs.desc: Comments about this mapping, including version notes, issues, scope limitations, and other important notes for usage.

ivardefs.name: identity
ivardefs.desc: An Internal id that is used to identify this mapping set when specific mappings are made.

ivardefs.name: name
ivardefs.desc: A name for the specification that is being mapped to.

ivardefs.name: uri
ivardefs.desc: An absolute URI that identifies the specification that this mapping is expressed to.

properties.desc: An external specification that the content is mapped to.
